And so, let's talk more about

00:27:26.616 --> 00:27:29.366 A:middle
what that means.

00:27:30.456 --> 00:27:31.786 A:middle
So, by indicating the primary

00:27:31.786 --> 00:27:33.086 A:middle
shortcut type, you're, kind of,

