use cases that you think your

00:27:36.206 --> 00:27:37.426 A:middle
users care about most.

00:27:37.426 --> 00:27:38.906 A:middle
And, this helps us expedite our

00:27:38.906 --> 00:27:39.766 A:middle
learning process.

